\"> エントリー・マイページはこちらから</p>\n            <ul class=\"c-openNav__subList u-alignItemsCenter p-flex\">\n              <li class=\"c-openNav__subItem\"><a class=\"p-button p-bgColorMain p-hover p-flex p-button--full p-button--small\" href=\"https://job.axol.jp/bx/s/tohogas_27/mypage/login\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"p-button__box p-flex\"><span class=\"p-button__text p-letterSpacing100 p-colorWhite t-fontWeight(600)\">2027卒</span><span class=\"p-hover__arrow p-button__arrow p-colorWhite\"><i class=\"on icon-arrow_right\"></i><i class=\"off icon-arrow_right p-floater\"></i></span></span></a></li>\n              <li class=\"c-openNav__subItem\"><a class=\"p-button p-bgColorMain p-hover p-flex p-button--full p-button--small\" href=\"https://axol.jp/zw/s/tohogas_28/entry/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"p-button__box p-flex\"><span class=\"p-button__text p-letterSpacing100 p-colorWhite t-fontWeight(600)\">2028卒</span><span class=\"p-hover__arrow p-button__arrow p-colorWhite\"><i class=\"on icon-arrow_right\"></i><i class=\"off icon-arrow_right p-floater\"></i></span></span></a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"c-openNav__item u-alignItemsCenter p-flex\">\n            <p class=\"c-openNav__title t-fontWeight(600)\"> イベント情報はこちらから</p>\n            <ul class=\"c-openNav__subList u-alignItemsCenter p-flex\">\n              <li class=\"c-openNav__subItem\"><a class=\"p-button p-bgColorMain p-hover p-flex p-button--full p-button--small\" href=\"https://www.tohogas.co.jp/compa/internship/university/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"p-button__box p-flex\"><span class=\"p-button__text p-letterSpacing100 p-colorWhite t-fontFamily(jost)\">EVENT</span><span class=\"p-hover__arrow p-button__arrow p-colorWhite\"><i class=\"on icon-arrow_right\"></i><i class=\"off icon-arrow_right p-floater\"></i></span></span></a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"c-openNav__bg\" data-button=\"hamburger-bg\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <main class=\"t-bg core-site-content u-overflowHidden\" id=\"main\">\n      <div class=\"indexMv\">\n        <div class=\"p-wrapper indexMv-wrapper p-wrapper--L\">\n          <h1 class=\"p-colorWhite p-letterSpacing100 p_catchphrase indexMv__title t-fontFamily(biz) t-lineHeight(1d6)\"><span class=\"p-flex p_catchphrase__block\"><span class=\"p_catchphrase__brackets p_catchphrase__brackets--left\"><img src=\"./images/common/deco-brackets01.svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></span><span>社会</span><span class=\"p_catchphrase__brackets p_catchphrase__brackets--right\"><img src=\"./images/common/deco-brackets02.svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></span>が、</span><span class=\"p_catchphrase__block p-flex\"><span>あなたの仕事場に。</span></span></h1>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"indexSlider\" data-slider=\"mv\">\n        <div class=\"swiper-wrapper indexSlider-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"swiper-slide indexSlider-wrapper__list\"><img src=\"./images/index-img-slider01.jpg\" width=\"520\" height=\"280\" alt=\"スライドA\"></div>\n          <div class=\"swiper-slide indexSlider-wrapper__list\"><img src=\"./images/index-img-slider02.jpg\" width=\"520\" height=\"280\" alt=\"スライドB\"></div>\n          <div class=\"swiper-slide indexSlider-wrapper__list\"><img src=\"./images/index-img-slider03.jpg\" width=\"520\" height=\"280\" alt=\"スライドC\"></div>\n          <div class=\"swiper-slide indexSlider-wrapper__list\"><img src=\"./images/index-img-slider04.jpg\" width=\"520\" height=\"280\" alt=\"スライドD\"></div>\n          <div class=\"swiper-slide indexSlider-wrapper__list\"><img src=\"./images/index-img-slider05.jpg\" width=\"520\" height=\"280\" alt=\"スライドE\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"indexRing\">\n        <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 2335.5 2127.2\">\n          <path d=\"M2227.9,174C2103,25.2,1887.7-25.4,1634.1,11.7c-64.3,9.4-131.3,24.5-199.9,45.2-244.7,73.7-509.6,217.6-755.5,423.9C93.2,972-162.4,1631.2,107.6,1953.1s963.7,184.5,1549.2-306.7c585.5-491.3,841.2-1150.5,571.1-1472.4ZM1645.9,1633.4c-577.4,484.5-1261.6,623-1525.2,308.8-263.6-314.2-8.4-963.9,569-1448.4,237.1-198.9,496.3-344.4,749.5-420.7,67.6-20.3,134-35.4,197.4-44.6,256.7-37.6,462.1,18,578.3,156.5,263.6,314.2,8.4,963.9-569,1448.4Z\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"indexMessage\">\n        <div class=\"p-wrapper p-wrapper--L\">\n          <div class=\"indexMessage-body\">\n            <p class=\"p-colorWhite u-uppercase indexMessage-body__flow u-weight300 t-fontFamily(jost) t-lineHeight(1d6)\">Energy<br>Life & business<br>Technology<br>Environment<br>Global</p>\n            <div class=\"indexMessage-contents p-colorWhite\">\n              <div class=\"indexMessage-contents__text p-letterSpacing50 p-letterSpacing100 t-lineHeight(2) t-fontWeight(600)\">\n                <p>エネルギーを、最適な形で人々に届ける。<br>くらしやビジネス、地域の未来を支える。<br>そうした使命の実現は、<br class=\"u-md\">「社会の問い」に目を向けることから始まります。<br>社会が急速に変化し、技術革新が進む中、<br class=\"u-md\">エネルギーや環境、地域社会の課題に<br>どんな解決策を導き出せるでしょうか。</p>\n                <p>「社会」というフィールドで、<br class=\"u-md\">あなたはどんなやりがいを見つけますか？<br>新しい価値を生み出すための挑戦を、<br class=\"u-md\">私たちと一緒に始めましょう。</p>\n              </div>\n              <p class=\"p-letterSpacing100 p-flex p-message t-fontFamily(biz) t-lineHeight(1d2)\"><span class=\"p-message__brackets\"><img src=\"./images/common/deco-brackets01.svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></span>社会<span class=\"p-message__brackets p-message__brackets--right\"><img src=\"./images/common/deco-brackets02.svg\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\"></span>が、あなたの仕事場に。</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <section class=\"indexNews\">\n        <div class=\"p-wrapper indexNews-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"indexNews-header\">\n            <h2 class=\"p-title u-uppercase p-colorWhite p-letterSpacing100 t-fontFamily(jost)\"><span>News</span></h2>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"indexNews-contents\">\n      